      <title>州长加文·纽瑟姆表示特朗普正在调查他和他的妻子</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/15/us/newsom-trump-doj-investigation.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆的助手表示，联邦特工在过去一周联系了几位与这对夫妇有关的人士。他批评此举是出于政治动机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/15/us/newsom-trump-doj-investigation.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 22:46:53 GMT</pubDate>
